title: Application For Business Visa

description.short: An application made by an individual to obtain a business visa for a specific country.
description.long: This application is made by an individual to obtain a business visa for a specific country. A business visa allows individuals to enter the country for business-related purposes, such as attending meetings, conferences, or negotiating contract
